<body>
    <section>
        <h1>Welcome to bricolo</h1>
        <br>
        <p><strong>bricolo</strong> is a streamlined development tool that enhances your PHP projects by automating common tasks like launching a PHP server, live-reloading with browser sync, and automatically compiling Sass and TypeScript. With a single command, you can set up a fully integrated development environment for both front-end and back-end workflows.</p>
        <br>
        <p>For a guide check out the <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/bricolo">documentation</a> on <img
        src="./npm.svg" height="15" />.</p>
    </section>
</body>
